## Derived work information

This repository contains modified files derived from the Apache Jena source
tree, specifically jena-fuseki2/jena-fuseki-docker at commit
f8ab05095fe532460b77e7d355fc27934eee9edd.

Those files were modified to support the build, packaging, and Docker Hub
publishing workflow used for the psiwon/jena-fuseki-docker image.
